Rejected from Hotel
attributes.characterDialogue: The original hotel they wanted to stay at rejected them

attributes.label: Restaurant "Above the skies"
attributes.characterDialogue: Now that you mention "skies", There was this one Restaurant called "Above the skies". Their name is weird, because when she passed it they only served sandwiches

attributes.label: The Viewing Platform
attributes.characterDialogue: She was at one of the Viewing Platform. The view was actually quite nice.

attributes.characterDialogue: They went to one Coffee Shop in the morning

attributes.label: Greenery
attributes.characterDialogue: She saw a lot of greenery

attributes.label: Harbor
attributes.characterDialogue: They avoided the Harbor, because the she hates the stinking fish

attributes.label: Fish & Crab Market
attributes.characterDialogue: They went past this and she hated the smell

attributes.label: Surfing Club
attributes.characterDialogue: She liked seeing hot surfers guys on the beach. There where really hot once, close to the Surfing Club in Misora. Her husband was mad at her for whistling but she doesnt understand why

attributes.label: Noise
attributes.characterDialogue: Everything was so loud and annoying

attributes.label: Bought Gem Jewellery
attributes.characterDialogue: She brought home some expensive Jewellery, like a pearl necklace and an emerald bracelet. Her husband said she doesn't need it but she believes otherwise

attributes.label: Style Boutiques
attributes.characterDialogue: They went to a lot of different Style Boutiques

attributes.label: Busses
attributes.characterDialogue: They went on a bus in the morning. The busses were  also with an audio guide, teeling them about the different buildings they passed

attributes.label: Galleries
attributes.characterDialogue: They first wanted to go inside a Gallery in morning but it wasn't open yet, So they headed to another

attributes.label: Boat Tours
attributes.characterDialogue: There are a lot of Boat Tours, but the only thing she got out of it was getting seasick. At least I didn't throw up like my husband

attributes.label: Stores
attributes.characterDialogue: They were in a bunch of "different" premium stores

attributes.label: Beaches
attributes.characterDialogue: They traveled along the beach because they wanted to get to a gallery at the end

attributes.label: Seafood Restaurant
attributes.characterDialogue: They ate together in one Seafood restaurant which was very close to the beach, It also offered a boat ride which she thought was interesting

attributes.label: The Cathedral on the hill
attributes.characterDialogue: It looked magnificent. They wanted to go but the were really hungry and wanted to eat something

attributes.label: Hotel: The Pearl
attributes.characterDialogue: She isn't a fan anymore, first they deny her stay and then they didn't even let her pass through. She had to take such a long path arounf the property to get where she wanted to go

attributes.label: Getting up early
attributes.characterDialogue: She always get's up early on vacation to be able to see as much as possible

attributes.label: Names of the shopping district streets
No sleep
attributes.characterDialogue: She couldn't get any sleep in the night it was horrible

attributes.label: Gondolas
attributes.characterDialogue: She took a gondola down the mountain

attributes.label: Hiking / Mountain
attributes.characterDialogue: When she went up the Mount Doom it was very annoying for her

attributes.label: Evening Restaurant
attributes.characterDialogue: She went to a Restaurant in the evening

attributes.label: Classy Lady
attributes.characterDialogue: She is so special and perfect, and people should respect that, but instead the whole city didnt show any respect

attributes.label: Her interest in vintage cars
attributes.characterDialogue: She loves cars especially vintage ones, shes disappointed of Misora. She heard of a car colletion but couldnt find one.

attributes.label: Discrimination
attributes.characterDialogue: On the Trip she was discriminated against for being a woman, because she wasnt able to access certain attractions

attributes.label: Annoying Husband
attributes.characterDialogue: She talks about her and her husband going on the trip together, but starts complaining about him immediately

attributes.label: Leaving the Hotel
attributes.characterDialogue: Here she is talking about the start of her day, how they took the bus and got coffee

attributes.label: Algea Bay
attributes.characterDialogue: They took a look at it and decided it wasn't worth going to

attributes.label: Spa
attributes.characterDialogue: She was at a Spa in Misora

attributes.label: Having Disagreements
attributes.characterDialogue: From time to time there are some times instances where her husband gets angry at her for no reason, but those can be quickly resolved and would never destroy the bond they share

attributes.label: Hotel "Cozy Camping"
attributes.characterDialogue: She is very glad she didn't stay there, They passed the Hotel and all of the Campers smelled horrible

attributes.label: Religious Sites
attributes.characterDialogue: She is a fan of religious sites and actually passed one in Misora, but there was a Wedding Happening so she couldn't enter

attributes.label: a shop for statues
attributes.characterDialogue: She went to a premium souvenier shop of statues for the different memorials. They didn't have names so she just picked the one which was prettiest, she also got a stone as a gift, which she is still confused by.

attributes.label: City Info
attributes.characterDialogue: They didnt receive as much info about the city as they would have liked, she complains that there wasn't any info point

attributes.label: Her plan for a private Mansion
Museum of Modern Art
attributes.characterDialogue: They saw it, but didn't go because "You can't buy the paintings there"

attributes.label: Friedas Garden Center
attributes.characterDialogue: They passed it but didnt go, she also talk about a weird fact about it

attributes.characterDialogue: They did not pass through a tunnel
